n started  Turn 5 he trades both Crackling Razormaw attacks once with Vicious Fledgling gets stealth again but he doesnt attack the 2nd time  I thought that he forgot to attack    Turn 6 turns out he is just BMing  he plays two Kill Command on my face then I just conceded  This is just a sample of the games I lose  this isnt fun and I feel like shit even if I won that match  I have played this game for 3 years and I have never had this kind of nuts hands that my opponents keep having most of the time  Fuck Hearthstone  I made the right choice to uninstall and move on  I dont need this game in my life\", \"commentId\": \"38074\", \"commentDate\": \"1495810812\"}, {\"comment\": \"Cant draw or mulligen any of the 6 1 drops in my deck to save my life  My opponents arcane missiles hit every target on my board  Mine cant hit any of the 4 minions of his board  and just goes straight face  How is it even possible to get this bad of RNG\", \"commentId\": \"38075\", \"commentDate\": \"1495812906\"}, {\"comment\": \"keeping a tally   played 12 games of casual so far today   8 of them have been against tier 2 or better ladder decks  fix this shit blizzard\", \"commentId\": \"38076\", \"commentDate\": \"1495813789\"}, {\"comment\": \"one big cancer game thats what this game is  FUCKING HUNTER GOT TYRANNUS OR WHATEVER  AND HE GOT THE RHINO THAT GIVES CHARGE BALANCED MOTHERFUCKING SHIT GAME NOTHING BUT LUCK SKILL DO NOT MATTER\", \"commentId\": \"38077\", \"commentDate\": \"1495814969\"}, {\"comment\": \"Ive only been playing in Ranked using my own Kazakus Priest build  I accepted one request and the guy basically told me to stop playing old cards lol\", \"commentId\": \"38078\", \"commentDate\": \"1495817336\"}, {\"comment\": \"When you have to keep your 78 mana cards in your mulligen because the chances of you actually drawing them during the game at 110 000 chance  Feels so fucking bad  I have a better chance of getting hit by an 18 wheeler truck than I do at drawing any card that I would need in any situation   BOTH arcane intellect  STACKED  one on top of another    last two cards in my deck  Went into fatigue  Give me the odds of something like this happening  I am the single    unluckiest player in this entire game  Kripp has absolutely nothing on me\", \"commentId\": \"38079\", \"commentDate\": \"1495818977\"}, {\"comment\": \"Hi  salty thread  its been a while  How are you Judging by the number of posts you got  you look in superb shape Me Oh  well    could stand a little bit more fairness in certain games  you know  Like this one I just lost to a shaman  who managed to summon between owned cards  discovered ones and totems something like 8 taunts    not to mention 3 healings to boot  Heh\", \"commentId\": \"38080\", \"commentDate\": \"1495821476\"}, {\"comment\": \"running into hunters and rogues and druids who always gets hungry crab in turn 1 to destroy all me murlocs and always matched against bad match ups druidddddddddddddddddddddd and hunterrr i hate this shit\", \"commentId\": \"38081\", \"commentDate\": \"1495822982\"}, {\"comment\": \"How do the stupid Hunters get Alley CatEVERYSTINKINGTIMEon the first turnGrrrrrrrrrrrr\", \"commentId\": \"38082\", \"commentDate\": \"1495830651\"}, {\"comment\": \"Thats a lie  Sometimes they get Jeweled Macaw\", \"commentId\": \"38083\", \"commentDate\": \"1495836536\"}]"